                <li>Identifying appropriate application categories</li>
                <li>Checking applications for completeness</li>
            </ul>
            <p class="mb-4">Unless otherwise agreed in writing, we do not:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
                <li>Submit applications on behalf of clients</li>
                <li>Communicate with immigration authorities</li>
                <li>Track application status</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Section 5: NO LEGAL OR IMMIGRATION ADVICE -->
